{"id":670512,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":11}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"136","ytitle":"","mtitle":"浪淘沙","ftitle":"","authors":["翁泽永"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"翁泽永"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去岁十一月，应邀赴四川乐山参加郭沫若研究学会年会，过渝访文化工作委员会——当年周恩来同志和郭老指挥的文化作战司令部旧址，有感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月照山城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光射太清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河耿耿耀群星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散蚕丛千载雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地光明!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首少年情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麾下一兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹心老去倍坚贞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好对长江东流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆我征程。"}]}